title: Initial D Collection
description:
The full anime Initial D collection. A few episodes are dubbed, but for the most part, assume Japanese audio with English subtitles. Does NOT contain the live action movie.

(1998) First Stage (26 episodes)
(1999) Second Stage (13 episodes)
(2000) Extra Stage (Full length movie)
(2001) Third Stage (Full length movie)
(2002) Battle Stage (Full length movie)
(2004) Fourth Stage (24 episodes)
(2007) Battle Stage 2 (Full length movie)
(2008) Extra Stage 2 (Full length movie)
(2012) Fifth Stage (14 episodes)
(2014) Final Stage (4 episodes)
